RawLine: TNPC_20043005,在下{color=#ff0000}江文順{/color}，真的是非常感謝少俠相處，還先給我桑葚吃，{p}否則我這吃素的，還沒打就先餓死了，因為這些山賊都大魚大肉的。,在下{color=#ff0000}江文顺{/color}，真的是非常感谢少侠相处，还先给我桑葚吃，{p}否则我这吃素的，还没打就先饿死了，因为这些山贼都大鱼大肉的。

Items.mt: My name is Jiang Wenshun, I am really grateful to the young knight for dealing with me and giving me mulberries to eat first, otherwise I, a vegetarian, would have died of hunger before I could fight, because these bandits are all big fish and big meat.
